sentences: He served in the Navy between 1955 and 1959, before relocating to New York City.

In 1971, Johnson released Fast and Funky, but his live playing gradually reduced.
A couple of low key albums appeared in the 1980s, before Johnson received more regular live work in the 1990s, particularly in Europe.
